{"tid":361140,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"No Game No Life Zero觀後感（無劇透）","createTime":"2017-08-16T00:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T00:39:23.000Z","uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b138fe4bd4c34b81fafab1552869dc03db8f4282","tid":361140,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:27:46.000Z","msg":"故事講小說第六本<br />\n幾千年前大戰時發生咩事同點結束<br />\n<br />\n畫面：<br />\n個畫面靚到出水<br />\n由其係戰鬥畫面簡直超曬班<br />\n<br />\n劇情：<br />\n成套電影得100分鐘<br />\n佢有好多嘢都無交代清楚<br />\n例如唯一神係點誕生同無詳細講星杯係咩<br />\n我有朋友淨係睇咗動畫去睇<br />\n成場都睇到黑人問號<br />\n<br />\n音樂：<br />\n同動畫一樣咁好<br />\n無乜好講<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n呢部係一部好鬱嘅電影<br />\n佢中間會派糖<br />\n但只係為咗令最尾更鬱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n我17號返嚟<br />\n18號上煙火<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bb3b8d302c5108e13557c87863b46625216707","tid":361140,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:39:23.000Z","msg":"你朋友唔明你咪解釋佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}